reviewText:
Roguelite" platformer with simple combat mechanics.

Disclaimer: this review is from someone who is not very goot at platformers.

Pros:
*Various modes;
*Responsive;
*Procedurelly generated levels forces to adapt;
*Traps require serious effort to time everything right;
*Leaderboards are a cool feature;
*Level creator;
*That visual awards for reaching LVL50 is trivial
